{"tid":2098654,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"巴西總統博爾索納羅中武肺","createTime":"2020-07-07T15:40:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T23:22:48.000Z","uid":122940,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cbe828edc2f3f3541196365a4effafdcee3c41db","tid":2098654,"uid":122940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:40:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/495216/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E5%8D%9A%E7%88%BE%E7%B4%A2%E7%B4%8D%E7%BE%85%E8%AD%89%E5%AF%A6%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F495216%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E5%258D%259A%25E7%2588%25BE%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E7%25B4%258D%25E7%25BE%2585%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivS%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=11da5897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/495216/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E5%8D%9A%E7%88%BE%E7%B4%A2%E7%B4%8D%E7%BE%85%E8%AD%89%E5%AF%A6%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA</a><br />\n<br />\n博爾索納羅稱，他在6日開始感到不適，及後經過病毒檢測後證實確診。他指自己正服用瘧疾藥羥氯喹（Hydroxychloroquine）及阿奇黴素（Azithromycin），並稱開始接受治療後，身體情況良好。不過原定到巴伊亞州（Bahia）視察的計劃則被迫取消。<br />\n<br />\n消息傳出後，泛美洲衛生組織祝願博爾索納羅可以早日康復，又認為事件反映當地的疫情仍未受到控制，強調當地需要更嚴格的社交距離措施。<br />\n<br />\n太睇少武肺的威力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc96e54f30ceb3ce070fc3bee25706331b2d558","tid":2098654,"uid":19728,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:41:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as